OL,3,CDumfries and Galloway Council leader
OL,4,Csteps down ahead of no confidence vote
OL,6,FThe leader of Dumfries and Galloway
OL,7,Fcouncil has stepped down less than an
OL,8,Fhour before she was due to face a no
OL,9,Fconfidence vote.
OL,11,FConservative councillor Gail Macgregor
OL,12,Fhas led the council since 2023.
OL,14,FIn a note to council officials, Cllr
OL,15,FMacgregor said she had decided to quit
OL,16,Fwith "the heaviest of hearts."
