OL,3,CDumfries and Galloway Council leader
OL,4,Csteps down ahead of no confidence vote
OL,6,FShe said: "It has been an absolute
OL,7,Fprivilege to serve the people of
OL,8,FDumfries and Galloway as Leader of the
OL,9,FCouncil for the past 26 months.
OL,10,F"During this time I have always tried
OL,11,Fto lead with a collaborative approach,
OL,12,Fand I will always do so for the good
OL,13,Fof the people we serve and the
OL,14,Fservices we provide."
OL,16,FA special meeting will take place this
OL,17,Fafternoon in which members are
OL,18,Fexpected to choose a new
OL,19,Fadministration.
